><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span># Mihail Maravelias</span><br><br><span>Software Engineering Student — University of Victoria  </span><br><span>Interested in Backend Engineering, Automation Systems, and Data Pipelines.</span><br><br><span>I build software that focuses on **automation, reliability, and clean system design**.</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## About Me</span><br><br><span>• Software Engineering student at the **University of Victoria (UVic)**  </span><br><span>• Experience building projects with **Python, Java, React, and SQL**  </span><br><span>• Interested in **automation pipelines, backend systems, and systems engineering**  </span><br><span>• Currently building projects that emphasize **clean architecture, testing, and scalability**</span><br><br><span>My goal is to build software that **automates real-world workflows and improves system efficiency.**</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## Technical Skills</span><br><br><span>### Languages</span><br><span>Python • Java • SQL • JavaScript</span><br><br><span>### Frameworks / Tools</span><br><span>React • Node.js • Git • REST APIs • FFmpeg</span><br><br><span>### Software Engineering</span><br><span>Unit Testing • Automation Pipelines • System Design • Debugging</span><br><br><span>### Systems / Engineering</span><br><span>Control Systems • Data Processing • Performance Analysis</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## Featured Projects</span><br><br><span>### Reddit-to-YouTube Automation Pipeline</span><br><span>Automates the creation of narrated storytelling videos from Reddit threads.</span><br><br><span>**Tech Stack:** Python, FFmpeg, React  </span><br><span>**Key Features**</span><br><span>- Converts Reddit posts into narrated videos automatically</span><br><span>- Generates captions and combines them with background footage</span><br><span>- Reduces manual video creation time from **~2 hours to ~3 minutes**</span><br><br><span>Repository:  </span><br><span>[reddit-youtube-automation](https://github.com/YOURUSERNAME/reddit-youtube-automation)</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>### Blackjack CLI Game (Test-Driven Development)</span><br><br><span>A command-line Blackjack game designed with **full automated test coverage**.</span><br><br><span>**Tech Stack:** Python, pytest</span><br><br><span>**Engineering Highlights**</span><br><span>- Achieved **100% branch coverage**</span><br><span>- Implemented robust decision logic for player/dealer interactions</span><br><span>- Demonstrates clean separation of game logic and UI</span><br><br><span>Repository:  </span><br><span>[blackjack-cli](https://github.com/YOURUSERNAME/blackjack-cli)</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>### Java Unit Testing Project (SENG 275)</span><br><br><span>A Java project focused on **professional testing practices**.</span><br><br><span>**Tech Stack:** Java, JUnit, Mockito</span><br><br><span>**Key Concepts**</span><br><span>- Mock-based testing</span><br><span>- Behavior verification</span><br><span>- High code coverage on decision logic</span><br><br><span>Repository:  </span><br><span>[seng275-testing](https://github.com/YOURUSERNAME/seng275-testing)</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>### Full-Stack Dashboard Prototype</span><br><br><span>Frontend dashboard designed for data visualization and system monitoring.</span><br><br><span>**Tech Stack:** React, TailwindCSS</span><br><br><span>**Highlights**</span><br><span>- Clean UI architecture</span><br><span>- Component-based design</span><br><span>- Responsive layout</span><br><br><span>Repository:  </span><br><span>[dashboard-prototype](https://github.com/YOURUSERNAME/dashboard-prototype)</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## What I'm Currently Working On</span><br><br><span>• Automation systems for content pipelines  </span><br><span>• Improving system architecture and backend design  </span><br><span>• Expanding portfolio with full-stack projects</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## Connect</span><br><br><span>LinkedIn: (add your link)  </span><br><span>GitHub: https://github.com/YOURUSERNAME</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
