"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span># Project Name</span><br><br><span>Short one sentence description of the project.</span><br><br><span>Example:</span><br><span>An automation pipeline that converts Reddit posts into fully produced YouTube storytelling videos.</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## Overview</span><br><br><span>This project was built to automate a multi-step content production workflow.</span><br><br><span>The system takes a Reddit post as input and automatically:</span><br><br><span>1. Converts the text to speech</span><br><span>2. Generates captions</span><br><span>3. Selects background footage</span><br><span>4. Combines assets into a final video</span><br><br><span>The goal was to build a system that demonstrates **automation pipelines, media processing, and backend orchestration.**</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## Tech Stack</span><br><br><span>Python  </span><br><span>React  </span><br><span>FFmpeg  </span><br><span>REST APIs</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## Key Features</span><br><br><span>• Automated content generation pipeline  </span><br><span>• Media processing using FFmpeg  </span><br><span>• Caption generation  </span><br><span>• Web interface for submitting posts  </span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## Architecture</span><br><br><span>The system consists of three main components:</span><br><br><span>Frontend  </span><br><span>React interface where users submit Reddit posts.</span><br><br><span>Backend Pipeline  </span><br><span>Python scripts process the text and generate media assets.</span><br><br><span>Media Processing  </span><br><span>FFmpeg combines narration, captions, and video.</span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>## Installation</span><br><br><span>Clone the repository</span><br></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
