<p data-start="4073" data-end="4147">"This student can design systems, write tested code, and finish projects."</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="4149" data-end="4176">You want recruiters to see:</p>
<p data-start="4178" data-end="4263">✔ Automation pipeline<br data-start="4199" data-end="4202">
✔ Testing<br data-start="4211" data-end="4214">
✔ Backend logic<br data-start="4229" data-end="4232">
✔ Frontend<br data-start="4242" data-end="4245">
✔ Systems thinking</p>
