<p data-start="134" data-end="224">I’ll give you a <strong data-start="150" data-end="181">real recruiter-style review</strong> and then tell you <strong data-start="200" data-end="223">exactly what to fix</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="226" data-end="229">
<h1 data-section-id="1ehkulg" data-start="231" data-end="273">First Impression (What a Recruiter Sees)</h1>
<p data-start="275" data-end="303">Right now your GitHub shows:</p>
<p data-start="305" data-end="318">Repositories:</p>
<ol data-start="319" data-end="401">
<li data-section-id="povqol" data-start="319" data-end="333">
<p data-start="322" data-end="333"><strong data-start="322" data-end="333">seng275</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13141qb" data-start="334" data-end="350">
<p data-start="337" data-end="350"><strong data-start="337" data-end="350">Portfolio</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wjo2p4" data-start="351" data-end="383">
<p data-start="354" data-end="383"><strong data-start="354" data-end="383">reddit-youtube-automation</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1y35lva" data-start="384" data-end="401">
<p data-start="387" data-end="401"><strong data-start="387" data-end="401">impact-cli</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="403" data-end="458">This is <strong data-start="411" data-end="429">a decent start</strong>, but there are a few issues:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1x8joxq" data-start="460" data-end="472">Problems</h3>
<ol data-start="474" data-end="983">
<li data-section-id="1rvel6q" data-start="474" data-end="589">
<p data-start="477" data-end="498"><strong data-start="477" data-end="498">No Profile README</strong></p>
<ul data-start="502" data-end="589">
<li data-section-id="1jr1rvs" data-start="502" data-end="537">
<p data-start="504" data-end="537">The top of your profile is empty.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="d44n1c" data-start="541" data-end="589">
<p data-start="543" data-end="589">Recruiters see nothing explaining who you are.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5dhui6" data-start="591" data-end="700">
<p data-start="594" data-end="626"><strong data-start="594" data-end="626">Repository names are unclear</strong></p>
<ul data-start="630" data-end="700">
<li data-section-id="1al9air" data-start="630" data-end="658">
<p data-start="632" data-end="658"><code data-start="632" data-end="643">Portfolio</code> tells nothing.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1m8yonq" data-start="662" data-end="700">
<p data-start="664" data-end="700"><code data-start="664" data-end="673">seng275</code> looks like class homework.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pcpmy4" data-start="702" data-end="812">
<p data-start="705" data-end="730"><strong data-start="705" data-end="730">Descriptions are weak</strong></p>
<ul data-start="734" data-end="812">
<li data-section-id="14tmmug" data-start="734" data-end="758">
<p data-start="736" data-end="758">Example: <code data-start="745" data-end="758">My projects</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fump2f" data-start="762" data-end="812">
<p data-start="764" data-end="812">That tells a recruiter <strong data-start="787" data-end="811">nothing about skills</strong>.</p>
