<hr data-start="985" data-end="988">
<h1 data-section-id="1v8qwab" data-start="990" data-end="1005">The Good News</h1>
<p data-start="1007" data-end="1046">You actually <strong data-start="1020" data-end="1045">do have good projects</strong>:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1ewujxz" data-start="1048" data-end="1061">Strongest</h3>
<p data-start="1062" data-end="1091"><strong data-start="1062" data-end="1091">reddit-youtube-automation</strong></p>
<p data-start="1093" data-end="1154">This is a <strong data-start="1103" data-end="1136">very strong portfolio project</strong> because it shows:</p>
<ul data-start="1156" data-end="1229">
<li data-section-id="544grb" data-start="1156" data-end="1168">
<p data-start="1158" data-end="1168">automation</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1k8enuq" data-start="1169" data-end="1184">
<p data-start="1171" data-end="1184">backend logic</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="kkj0av" data-start="1185" data-end="1203">
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1203">media processing</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fed7pp" data-start="1204" data-end="1229">
<p data-start="1206" data-end="1229">full-stack architecture</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1231" data-end="1292">That is <strong data-start="1239" data-end="1291">exactly the kind of project that gets interviews</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1294" data-end="1297">
<h1 data-section-id="170rcix" data-start="1299" data-end="1331">What You Should Do Immediately</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="3ecw8e" data-start="1333" data-end="1358">1. Rename Repositories</h2>
<p data-start="1360" data-end="1373">Better names:</p>
