<p data-start="1550" data-end="1560">instead of</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1562" data-end="1577"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>seng275</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1579" data-end="1627">Recruiters should <strong data-start="1597" data-end="1626">instantly know what it is</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1629" data-end="1632">
<h1 data-section-id="1gdtasa" data-start="1634" data-end="1666">2. Fix Repository Descriptions</h1>
<p data-start="1668" data-end="1697">Right now they are too vague.</p>
<p data-start="1699" data-end="1723">Examples you should use:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1c5gyd2" data-start="1725" data-end="1754">reddit-youtube-automation</h3>
<p data-start="1756" data-end="1764">Current:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1765" data-end="1836">
<p data-start="1767" data-end="1836">A full-stack dashboard to manage Reddit-to-YouTube content automation</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="1838" data-end="1845">Better:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1847" data-end="1982">
<p data-start="1849" data-end="1982">Full-stack automation pipeline that converts Reddit threads into narrated YouTube videos using Python, FFmpeg, and a React dashboard.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1984" data-end="1987">
<h3 data-section-id="1x1yl2n" data-start="1989" data-end="2003">impact-cli</h3>
<p data-start="2005" data-end="2024">Better description:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2026" data-end="2121">
<p data-start="2028" data-end="2121">Java command-line tool for interacting with the Impact.com API and automating workflow tasks.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2123" data-end="2126">
<h3 data-section-id="1cddt5e" data-start="2128" data-end="2150">java-testing-suite</h3>
<p data-start="2152" data-end="2159">Better:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2161" data-end="2271">
<p data-start="2163" data-end="2271">Java testing project demonstrating unit testing, mocking, and behavior verification using JUnit and Mockito.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2273" data-end="2276">
<h1 data-section-id="9icgaj" data-start="2278" data-end="2300">3. Pin Your Projects</h1>
<p data-start="2302" data-end="2341">On GitHub you can <strong data-start="2320" data-end="2340">pin repositories</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="2343" data-end="2353">Pin these:</p>
<p data-start="2355" data-end="2510">1️⃣ reddit-youtube-automation<br data-start="2384" data-end="2387">
2️⃣ impact-cli<br data-start="2401" data-end="2404">
3️⃣ java-testing-suite<br data-start="2426" data-end="2429">
4️⃣ blackjack-cli (when you upload it)<br data-start="2467" data-end="2470">
5️⃣ dashboard-prototype (future project)</p>
<p data-start="2512" data-end="2566">Pinned projects appear <strong data-start="2535" data-end="2565">at the top of your profile</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2568" data-end="2571">
<h1 data-section-id="lddzin" data-start="2573" data-end="2615">4. Add a Profile README (Most Important)</h1>
