"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span># Mihail Maravelias</span><br><br><span>Software Engineering Student at the University of Victoria.</span><br><br><span>I build software focused on automation systems, backend engineering, and data pipelines.</span><br><br><span>## Tech Stack</span><br><br><span>Python  </span><br><span>Java  </span><br><span>React  </span><br><span>SQL  </span><br><br><span>Tools  </span><br><span>Git • REST APIs • FFmpeg</span><br><br><span>## Featured Projects</span><br><br><span>### Reddit-to-YouTube Automation</span><br><span>Full-stack automation system that converts Reddit posts into narrated YouTube videos.</span><br><br><span>Tech:</span><br><span>Python • React • FFmpeg</span><br><br><span>### Java Testing Suite</span><br><span>Unit testing project demonstrating professional testing practices using JUnit and Mockito.</span><br><br><span>### Impact CLI</span><br><span>Java command-line tool for interacting with APIs and automating workflow tasks.</span><br><br><span>## Interests</span><br><br><span>Automation Systems  </span><br><span>Backend Engineering  </span><br><span>Systems Programming  </span><br><span>Software Architecture</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
