<ul data-start="107" data-end="236">
<li data-section-id="mhlzb2" data-start="107" data-end="122">
<p data-start="109" data-end="122">Your <strong data-start="114" data-end="122">name</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11u9rwm" data-start="123" data-end="171">
<p data-start="125" data-end="171">Your <strong data-start="130" data-end="171">degree (Software Engineering at UVic)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="o7e90x" data-start="172" data-end="194">
<p data-start="174" data-end="194">Your <strong data-start="179" data-end="194">focus areas</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1maqs5p" data-start="195" data-end="216">
<p data-start="197" data-end="216">Your <strong data-start="202" data-end="216">tech stack</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="41ncin" data-start="217" data-end="236">
<p data-start="219" data-end="236">Your <strong data-start="224" data-end="236">projects</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="238" data-end="306">That alone already makes your profile <strong data-start="276" data-end="302">much more professional</strong>. 👍</p>
<p data-start="308" data-end="412">But there are <strong data-start="322" data-end="342">3 small upgrades</strong> that would make this look <strong data-start="369" data-end="411">much more polished and recruiter-level</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="414" data-end="417">
<h1 data-section-id="1qv30pc" data-start="419" data-end="457">1. Add a Short “Elevator Pitch” Line</h1>
<p data-start="459" data-end="548">Right now it jumps straight into description. Add a <strong data-start="511" data-end="531">strong one-liner</strong> under your name.</p>
<p data-start="550" data-end="576">Replace the top with this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="578" data-end="895"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Markdown</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span># Mihail Maravelias</span><br><br><span>Software Engineering Student at the University of Victoria.</span><br><br><span>I design and build software systems focused on **automation, backend infrastructure, and data pipelines**.</span><br><br><span>My projects emphasize **clean architecture, automation workflows, and production-style engineering practices.**</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="897" data-end="946">This makes it sound <strong data-start="917" data-end="945">more engineering-focused</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="948" data-end="951">
<h1 data-section-id="ag3cec" data-start="953" data-end="988">2. Improve the Tech Stack Section</h1>
<p data-start="990" data-end="1056">Right now it is just a list. Recruiters prefer <strong data-start="1037" data-end="1055">grouped skills</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1058" data-end="1081">Change this section to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1083" data-end="1299"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Markdown</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>## Tech Stack</span><br><br><span>Languages  </span><br><span>Python • Java • SQL • JavaScript</span><br><br><span>Frontend  </span><br><span>React</span><br><br><span>Tools  </span><br><span>Git • REST APIs • FFmpeg</span><br><br><span>Engineering Practices  </span><br><span>Unit Testing • Automation Pipelines • Debugging • System Design</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1301" data-end="1357">This makes it feel <strong data-start="1320" data-end="1356">more structured and professional</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1359" data-end="1362">
<h1 data-section-id="xodd14" data-start="1364" data-end="1401">3. Improve the Project Descriptions</h1>
<p data-start="1403" data-end="1473">Recruiters scan quickly. The descriptions should highlight <strong data-start="1462" data-end="1472">impact</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1475" data-end="1513">Replace the project section with this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1515" data-end="2170"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Markdown</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>## Featured Projects</span><br><br><span>### Reddit-to-YouTube Automation</span><br><span>Full-stack automation system that converts Reddit posts into narrated YouTube videos.</span><br><br><span>Tech: Python • React • FFmpeg</span><br><br><span>Highlights</span><br><span>• Automated content generation pipeline  </span><br><span>• Media processing with FFmpeg  </span><br><span>• Reduces manual video production from hours to minutes  </span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>### Java Testing Suite</span><br><span>Java testing project demonstrating professional unit testing practices using JUnit and Mockito.</span><br><br><span>Highlights</span><br><span>• Mock-based testing  </span><br><span>• Behavior verification  </span><br><span>• High coverage on decision logic  </span><br><br><span>---</span><br><br><span>### Impact CLI</span><br><span>Java command-line tool for interacting with APIs and automating workflow tasks.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2172" data-end="2224">Now it reads more like <strong data-start="2195" data-end="2223">a professional portfolio</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2226" data-end="2229">
<h1 data-section-id="1ppjbbi" data-start="2231" data-end="2283">4. Add One More Section (Very Good for Recruiters)</h1>
<p data-start="2285" data-end="2303">At the bottom add:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2305" data-end="2488"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Markdown</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>## Currently Working On</span><br><br><span>• Automation pipelines for media generation  </span><br><span>• Backend systems and APIs  </span><br><span>• Expanding portfolio projects for software engineering internships</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2490" data-end="2536">Recruiters like seeing <strong data-start="2513" data-end="2535">active development</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2538" data-end="2541">
<h1 data-section-id="fbfpsv" data-start="2543" data-end="2574">5. One Small Cosmetic Upgrade</h1>
