y good idea</strong>. A smaller, cleaner GitHub is <strong data-start="67" data-end="108">much better than lots of random repos</strong>. Recruiters usually look at <strong data-start="137" data-end="157">3–6 projects max</strong>, so anything irrelevant just adds noise.</p>
<p data-start="200" data-end="240">From the screenshot, you currently have:</p>
<ol data-start="242" data-end="324">
<li data-section-id="povqol" data-start="242" data-end="256">
<p data-start="245" data-end="256"><strong data-start="245" data-end="256">seng275</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13141qb" data-start="257" data-end="273">
<p data-start="260" data-end="273"><strong data-start="260" data-end="273">Portfolio</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wjo2p4" data-start="274" data-end="306">
<p data-start="277" data-end="306"><strong data-start="277" data-end="306">reddit-youtube-automation</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1y35lva" data-start="307" data-end="324">
<p data-start="310" data-end="324"><strong data-start="310" data-end="324">impact-cli</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="326" data-end="369">Let’s evaluate them like a recruiter would.</p>
<hr data-start="371" data-end="374">
<h1 data-section-id="h3o2ut" data-start="376" data-end="400">Keep These (Important)</h1>
<h3 data-section-id="hduiej" data-start="402" data-end="437">1️⃣ reddit-youtube-automation</h3>
<p data-start="438" data-end="446"><strong data-start="438" data-end="446">KEEP</strong></p>
<p data-start="448" data-end="478">This is your <strong data-start="461" data-end="477">best project</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="480" data-end="484">Why:</p>
<ul data-start="485" data-end="560">
<li data-section-id="1i9fqpk" data-start="485" data-end="497">
<p data-start="487" data-end="497">full-stack</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="544grb" data-start="498" data-end="510">
<p data-start="500" data-end="510">automation</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2z3lrq" data-start="511" data-end="531">
<p data-start="513" data-end="531">real-world problem</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o40yiw" data-start="532" data-end="560">
<p data-start="534" data-end="560">uses multiple technologies</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="562" data-end="613">This should actually become your <strong data-start="595" data-end="612">flagship repo</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="615" data-end="618">
<h3 data-section-id="1eq00fl" data-start="620" data-end="640">2️⃣ impact-cli</h3>
<p data-start="641" data-end="649"><strong data-start="641" data-end="649">KEEP</strong></p>
<p data-start="651" data-end="655">Why:</p>
<ul data-start="656" data-end="737">
<li data-section-id="117mxdv" data-start="656" data-end="693">
<p data-start="658" data-end="693">CLI tools are good portfolio pieces</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="975mti" data-start="694" data-end="713">
<p data-start="696" data-end="713">shows Java skills</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="416aey" data-start="714" data-end="737">
<p data-start="716" data-end="737">shows API interaction</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="739" data-end="742">
<h1 data-section-id="havt6f" data-start="744" data-end="770">Maybe Keep (But Improve)</h1>
<h3 data-section-id="125ml06" data-start="772" data-end="787">3️⃣ seng275</h3>
<p data-start="789" data-end="847">Right now the name makes it look like <strong data-start="827" data-end="846">course homework</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="849" data-end="857">Options:</p>
<p data-start="859" data-end="906">Option A (Better):<br>
Rename it to something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="908" data-end="934"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>java-testing-suite</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="936" data-end="938">or</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="940" data-end="974"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>java-unit-testing-practice</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="976" data-end="1049">That makes it look like <strong data-start="1000" data-end="1048">an engineering project instead of class work</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1051" data-end="1054">
<h1 data-section-id="5mmsk4" data-start="1056" data-end="1074">Delete or Rework</h1>
<h3 data-section-id="1ikeyuc" data-start="1076" data-end="1093">4️⃣ Portfolio</h3>
<p data-start="1095" data-end="1113">Right now it says:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1115" data-end="1128">
<p data-start="1117" data-end="1128">My projects</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="1130" data-end="1159">That repo isn’t adding value.</p>
<p data-start="1161" data-end="1182">You have two options.</p>
<p data-start="1184" data-end="1216"><strong data-start="1184" data-end="1203">Option A (Best)</strong><br data-start="1203" data-end="1206">
Delete it.</p>
<p data-start="1218" data-end="1286"><strong data-start="1218" data-end="1230">Option B</strong><br data-start="1230" data-end="1233">
Turn it into a <strong data-start="1248" data-end="1279">real portfolio website repo</strong> later.</p>
<p data-start="1288" data-end="1319">For now, I would <strong data-start="1305" data-end="1318">delete it</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1321" data-end="1324">
<h1 data-section-id="1lvul60" data-start="1326" data-end="1364">What a Clean GitHub Should Look Like</h1>
<p data-start="1366" data-end="1426">A strong student GitHub usually has <strong data-start="1402" data-end="1425">4–6 strong projects</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1428" data-end="1443">Example layout:</p>
<p data-start="1445" data-end="1588">1️⃣ reddit-youtube-automation<br data-start="1474" data-end="1477">
2️⃣ impact-cli<br data-start="1491" data-end="1494">
3️⃣ java-testing-suite<br data-start="1516" data-end="1519">
4️⃣ blackjack-cli (your Python project)<br data-start="1558" data-end="1561">
5️⃣ jobtrackr (SQL project)</p>
<p data-start="1590" data-end="1601">That shows:</p>
<ul data-start="1603" data-end="1665">
<li data-section-id="2q6buk" data-start="1603" data-end="1611">
<p data-start="1605" data-end="1611">Python</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j3vxn8" data-start="1612" data-end="1618">
<p data-start="1614" data-end="1618">Java</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19yik5h" data-start="1619" data-end="1630">
<p data-start="1621" data-end="1630">CLI tools</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="544grb" data-start="1631" data-end="1643">
<p data-start="1633" data-end="1643">automation</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jq4zdq" data-start="1644" data-end="1655">
<p data-start="1646" data-end="1655">databases</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15lqjcu" data-start="1656" data-end="1665">
<p data-start="1658" data-end="1665">testing</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1667" data-end="1681">Very balanced.</p>
<hr data-start="1683" data-end="1686">
<h1 data-section-id="ph7vtj" data-start="1688" data-end="1716">How to Delete a Repository</h1>
<p data-start="1718" data-end="1733">Go to the repo.</p>
<p data-start="1735" data-end="1741">Click:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1743" data-end="1759"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Settings</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1761" data-end="1785">Scroll all the way down.</p>
<p data-start="1787" data-end="1793">Click:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1795" data-end="1825"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Delete this repository</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1827" data-end="1880">GitHub will ask you to type the repo name to confirm.</p>
<hr data-start="1882" data-end="1885">
<h1 data-section-id="biuxrh" data-start="1887" data-end="1902">Important Tip</h1>
<p data-start="1904" data-end="1990"><strong data-start="1904" data-end="1950">Never delete a repo that shows real skills</strong>, even if it's messy.<br data-start="1971" data-end="1974">
Instead you can:</p>
<ul data-start="1992" data-end="2041">
<li data-section-id="b8vuyt" data-start="1992" data-end="2003">
<p data-start="1994" data-end="2003">rename it</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kfy3u9" data-start="2004" data-end="2024">
<p data-start="2006" data-end="2024">improve the README</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ybvd6h" data-start="2025" data-end="2041">
<p data-start="2027" data-end="2041">clean the code</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2043" data-end="2084">Deleting is only good for <strong data-start="2069" data-end="2083">junk repos</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2086" data-end="2089">
<h1 data-section-id="w0j3kz" data-start="2091" data-end="2118">My Recommendation For You</h1>
<p data-start="2120" data-end="2125">Keep:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2127" data-end="2188"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>reddit-youtube-automation</span><br><span>impact-cli</span><br><span>seng275 (rename)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2190" data-end="2197">Delete:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2199" data-end="2216"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Portfolio</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2218" data-end="2233">Then later add:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2235" data-end="2266"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>blackjack-cli</span><br><span>jobtrackr</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2268" data-end="2326">That will make your GitHub look <strong data-start="2300" data-end="2325">much more intentional</strong>.</p>
