2️⃣ impact-cli<br data-start="3066" data-end="3069">
3️⃣ arm-assembly-project<br data-start="3093" data-end="3096">
4️⃣ java-testing-suite<br data-start="3118" data-end="3121">
5️⃣ blackjack-cli</p>
<p data-start="3142" data-end="3153">That shows:</p>
